list.name: Start
list.query:
SELECT
  test_started  AS time,
  run_id AS text,
  test_name
FROM
  jmresults_tests
WHERE
  timestamp_sec >= toDateTime($from) AND timestamp_sec < toDateTime($to)

  test_started  AS time,
  run_id AS text,
  test_name
FROM
  jmresults_tests
WHERE
  timestamp_sec >= toDateTime(1608545586) AND timestamp_sec < toDateTime(1608549186)

targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
SELECT
    $timeSeries as t,
    count(timestamp_millis)/$agr as "Requests per second"
FROM jmresults_statistic
WHERE $timeFilter AND sampler_type = 'REQUEST'
AND profile_name ='$profile' and run_id IN ($runid)
GROUP BY t
ORDER BY t
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT
    (intDiv(toUInt32(timestamp_sec), 10) * 10) * 1000 as t,
    count(timestamp_millis)/10 as "Requests per second"
FROM jmresults_statistic
WHERE timestamp_sec BETWEEN toDateTime(1608189880) AND toDateTime(1608200577) AND sampler_type = 'REQUEST'
AND profile_name ='TEST' and run_id IN ('R002','R001')
GROUP BY t
ORDER BY t

targets.formattedQuery:
SELECT sample_label,
       sum(points_count) as "Total",
       count(points_count) as "TotalRecs",
       sum(points_count)/count(points_count) as "Compress",
       avg(average_time)/1000 as "AvgResp",
       min(average_time)/1000 as "MinResp",
       max(average_time)/1000 as "MaxResp",
       quantile(0.9)(average_time) as "90perc",
       quantile(0.95)(average_time) as "95perc",
       quantile(0.97)(average_time) as "97perc",
       quantile(0.99)(average_time) as "99perc",
       sum(errors_count) as "Errors",
       (sum(errors_count)/sum(points_count)) as "ErrorRate"
from jmresults
WHERE  profile_name ='TEST' and run_id='TEST'
GROUP BY sample_label;
targets.query:
SELECT sample_label,
       count(timestamp_sec) as total,
       min(timestamp_sec) as start,
       max(timestamp_sec) as stop,
       total/toUInt64(stop-start) as rate,
       avg(average_time)/1000 as "AvgResp",
       median(average_time)/1000 as "MedianResp",
       quantileTDigest(0.9)(average_time)/1000 as "90perc",
       quantileTDigest(0.95)(average_time)/1000 as "95perc",
       sum(errors_count) as "Errors",
       (sum(errors_count)/count(timestamp_sec)) as "ErrorRate"
from jmresults_statistic
WHERE  $timeFilter AND profile_name ='$profile' and run_id IN ($runid) and not like(sample_label, 'http%') and sampler_type = '$sampler_type'
GROUP BY sample_label
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT sample_label,
       count(timestamp_sec) as total,
       min(timestamp_sec) as start,
       max(timestamp_sec) as stop,
       total/toUInt64(stop-start) as rate,
       avg(average_time)/1000 as "AvgResp",
       median(average_time)/1000 as "MedianResp",
       quantileTDigest(0.9)(average_time)/1000 as "90perc",
       quantileTDigest(0.95)(average_time)/1000 as "95perc",
       sum(errors_count) as "Errors",
       (sum(errors_count)/count(timestamp_sec)) as "ErrorRate"
from jmresults_statistic
WHERE  timestamp_sec BETWEEN toDateTime(1608189880) AND toDateTime(1608200577) AND profile_name ='TEST' and run_id IN ('R002','R001') and not like(sample_label, 'http%') and sampler_type = 'REQUEST'
GROUP BY sample_label
